{"tid":475560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擁近250萬存款也申請公屋！  因暪報判囚兩周獲緩刑、罰款1.3萬","createTime":"2017-11-21T08:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T16:11:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8567a7e77d032b932557d1e19907cfed050c16","tid":475560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"一名公屋申請人因填寫申請表時，隱瞞擁有近250萬元存款，昨被判監14天及罰款1.3萬元，緩刑2年。<br />\n<br />\n被告去年約7月向房屋署遞交一份公屋申請表，申報只擁有約2.7萬元銀行存款。房署同年9月調查揭發，被告只申報了一間銀行的戶口，而刻意隱瞞在另一間銀行的綜合理財戶口，當中包含3個港元戶口及一個人民幣存款戶口，金額共達約248萬元。<br />\n<br />\n被告違反《房屋條例》第26（1）（c）條，被控明知而作出虛假陳述，昨在九龍城裁判法院聆訊。裁判官考慮案情嚴重，判被告罰款1.3萬元及監禁14天，緩刑24個月。<br />\n<br />\n房屋署提醒公屋申請人，如違反《房屋條例》第26（1）（c）條，即在申請公屋時明知而向香港房屋委員會作出虛假的陳述，一經定罪最高可判罰款5萬元及監禁6個月，所登記的公屋申請亦會被取消。"},{"pid":"6f93ed0e1f6b745f4c5d8ae6de8dbc18f9a89c6f","tid":475560,"uid":33424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:38:12.000Z","msg":"好奇想知房署點查到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正路唔會就咁問金管局"},{"pid":"c6822436504e3a2095a07cf1f9da5383ecf6c009","tid":475560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇想知房署點查到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正路唔會就咁問金管局</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定有人篤啦"},{"pid":"fd6bf7a6446230b7fc351485957185ff75e47bde","tid":475560,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇想知房署點查到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正路唔會就咁問金管局</blockquote><br />\n正路房署唔會做野<br />\n俾你直接申請到煩d定查你家宅煩d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd4764a7bda246a3beb4278b4df0f9eb044878a","tid":475560,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"天才"},{"pid":"7ed0a6ab4b5fd99209f7e38e3a7dc128ce425119","tid":475560,"uid":8710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"係咪中六合彩"},{"pid":"a135e07047c0d1563f83ad9fc4f8beed25251f96","tid":475560,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"有2百幾萬仲申請公屋 衰左都係判罰萬幾同坐14日 仲要有得緩刑 怪唔得班仆街係咁呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9605e813c5550c247d76a0171f99559af8ca0de1","tid":475560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有2百幾萬仲申請公屋 衰左都係判罰萬幾同坐14日 仲要有得緩刑 怪唔得班仆街係咁呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmoral hazard"},{"pid":"539cc832220597f2c014c476746d42ce21c5a7d7","tid":475560,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會知？"},{"pid":"a7f6ba3290c2046a98c141a2fe4e43fbcb3d7dd3","tid":475560,"uid":72519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"其實放係銀行，戶口有哂個人資料唔會好易check到咩？"},{"pid":"756a7632f7374d07deae07e963c0f3ac6175384a","tid":475560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實放係銀行，戶口有哂個人資料唔會好易check到咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會, 除非你去鄰近國家開戶口, 放入外國銀行"},{"pid":"df04698b84f36e1be53e051e6b9700dd33a32e0b","tid":475560,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171121/large/1511263837_8208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171121%2Flarge%2F1511263837_8208.jpg&h=18bc4c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">29歲有248萬！</span></span>"}]}